<a id="13"></a>

## 13. Setup Local

```bash
git clone git@github.com:vibecoding/llm-seo-score.git
cd llm-seo-score
cp .env.example .env
docker compose up -d         # supabase-local, redis, grafana+otel
poetry install
prefect worker start --pool default
prefect deployment run demo-one-domain   # smoke test
```

